The internet may seem like a technology built solely to line the pockets of Big Tech, but there are good reasons to be sceptical of this conclusion. Read the introductory first blog from Liam Mullally that opens up paths untravelled. https://buff.ly/3Ei6wM9

Here’s your brain stretch for the day. Do you recognize what these tech objects are? Take a guess below. We’ll reveal the answer tomorrow. Oh, and if you are still depending on one of these, maybe it’s time to upgrade your technology. Give us a call. We can help – 317-857-0150. #smallbusiness #ITsmallbusiness #techsupport

Thanks to #55KRC, Brian Thomas, and Joe Strecker for another #Tech Friday. Listen at the link below and join us every Friday at 6:30 AM for helpful #technology news and tips to help you, your family and your organization be more productive AND secure.
